{"tid":734802,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚引玉] 返工撚 健康早餐推介","createTime":"2018-07-09T03:29:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T03:36:04.000Z","uid":7615,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"84ffc57b643620704c74267d11a915d3a5830aa1","tid":734802,"uid":7615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:29:13.000Z","msg":"雞絲雞蛋麥皮+燕麥糠 香蕉一條<br />\n準備時間：8-15分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：蛋白質碳水維他命膳食纖維乜鳩都有<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：麥皮都幾飽肚 延遲饑餓感<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ：準備時間頗長（對某啲人黎講）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：麥皮唔係個個都放到入口<br />\n麥皮唔好煮太耐 可以落少少鹽<br />\n雞最好走皮<br />\n推薦指數：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n牛油果花生醬全麥麵包 低糖/無糖豆漿一杯<br />\n準備時間：&lt;5分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：牛油果食落幾似三文魚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：一樽花生醬 可以整好多餐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ：牛油果花生醬高卡路里 份量要控制得好好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：豆漿低糖/無糖 有人會覺得淡而無味<br />\n牛油果最多半個 花生醬最多20克<br />\n花生醬最好買一粒粒<br />\n推薦指數：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n面包鋪求其買既提子麥包 高鈣脫脂奶<br />\n準備時間：30s-1mins不等（視乎排隊人數）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：最方便<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ：唔知包鋪落幾多油糖去整個包<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：奶糖份都幾高<br />\n腿蛋治都可以 不過要小心加工肉唔健康<br />\n推薦指數：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n茶記沙嗲牛出前一丁 火腿奄列 牛油方包 凍奶茶<br />\n準備時間：20-30分鐘（由落餐至埋單）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：人間美食<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：乜鳩都高 卡路里油鹽糖<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：比上面啲早餐貴<br />\n一個月一至兩次好啦<br />\n推薦指數：<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歡迎巴絲提供更多健康早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以上內容如有錯 屌得細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f651a22feaf87eb7fe5edc1677f28f77a47bda","tid":734802,"uid":85564,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:18:32.000Z","msg":"鮮奶蛋花麥皮<br />\n<br />\n250ml牛奶+兩隻蛋溝埋<br />\n<br />\n倒落煲 煲至水滾後熄火<br />\n<br />\n之後落40-50 gram麥皮<br />\n<br />\n攪拌<br />\n<br />\n最後再落一圈至二圈低脂煉奶<br />\n<br />\n再攪拌，完成<br />\n<br />\n準備時間: 5-8分鐘"},{"pid":"eebcc4ee5b7b691825f7396296559dda38433597","tid":734802,"uid":7974,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T06:06:08.000Z","msg":"紫薯+烚蛋<br />\n<br />\n沖一沖舊紫薯 再放落鑊到蒸<br />\n之後去做自己野 例如刷牙洗臉化妝<br />\n差唔多蒸完前五分鐘再放隻蛋落去烚<br />\n之後出門口個時拎一拎就返得工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返到office再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個組合食左幾個月<br />\n<br />\n準備時間：1分鐘<br />\n等候時間約15-20分鐘<br />\n想再快d就揀d細舊既紫薯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時前一晚裝定d麥皮同無糖可可粉落玻璃兜到，早上再烚隻蛋返公司食"},{"pid":"c2a6cd823bee1dd0d2f1c79eb1b6e5983a1f13b7","tid":734802,"uid":7615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T12:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f7ce37bad76b1f1579cffe278248f7ace1543b","tid":734802,"uid":1400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:09:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2661fdd6ba39e0e2791c968503487f5063d6670","tid":734802,"uid":7615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T01:39:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6bfc85459031a91b3753bb84426de033c1268cb","tid":734802,"uid":31509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"84ffc57b643620704c74267d11a915d3a5830aa1","tid":734802,"uid":7615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:29:13.000Z","msg":"雞絲雞蛋麥皮+燕麥糠 香蕉一條<br />\n準備時間：8-15分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：蛋白質碳水維他命膳食纖維乜鳩都有<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：麥皮都幾飽肚 延遲饑餓感<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ：準備時間頗長（對某啲人黎講）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：麥皮唔係個個都放到入口<br />\n麥皮唔好煮太耐 可以落少少鹽<br />\n雞最好走皮<br />\n推薦指數：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n牛油果花生醬全麥麵包 低糖/無糖豆漿一杯<br />\n準備時間：&lt;5分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：牛油果食落幾似三文魚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：一樽花生醬 可以整好多餐<br />