.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：奶糖份都幾高<br />\n腿蛋治都可以 不過要小心加工肉唔健康<br />\n推薦指數：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n茶記沙嗲牛出前一丁 火腿奄列 牛油方包 凍奶茶<br />\n準備時間：20-30分鐘（由落餐至埋單）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：人間美食<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：乜鳩都高 卡路里油鹽糖<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：比上面啲早餐貴<br />\n一個月一至兩次好啦<br />\n推薦指數：<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歡迎巴絲提供更多健康早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以上內容如有錯 屌得細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T02:59:51.000Z","msg":"茶記沙嗲牛同花生醬不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下係小弟建議<br />\n一：牛油果（可以撈 1tbsp mayonnaise）+燉蛋片+麥包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n二：無糖yogurt+blueberry+蕉+即食麥皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n三：牛奶薏米粥，唔夠飽就食隻燉蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57eb81c616de61ae9dd8a6bcdba3c495007fe6f2","tid":734802,"uid":191633,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"23eb53f4699db060435023c9dbe878dab779effc","tid":734802,"uid":103618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T02:45:31.000Z","msg":"點睇全脂奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  上網睇新聞 話全脂奶可能比低脂奶更健康 因為添加物少d 又飽肚d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T03:01:50.000Z","msg":"全脂奶一定係健康啲<br />\n尤其係牛奶，非牛奶飲品"},{"pid":"f20f0fa1a8395b7d48c2d2be448e7167cdf0846c","tid":734802,"uid":1400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3b212faf8abe3491f1d88968bbc0c36bb9b2173","t